 barriers and mixing classical music into the soundtrack of everyday life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2020) 0aAbsolute music. 0aMP3 (Audio coding standard)xSocial aspects. 0aMusic and technology. 0aMusicxPhilosophy and aesthetics. 0aPerformance practice (Music)xHistoryx20th century. 0aPerformance practice (Music)xHistoryy20th century. 0aSound recordingsxSocial aspects. 0aSoundxRecording and reproducingxDigital techniques. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Classical.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook Package 2000-2015z978311066334108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520945692423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520945692.jpg  a978-3-11-066334-1  UC Press eBook Package 2000-2015c2000d2015  a978-3-11-069042-2  UC Press eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles